{"tid":2215171,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵套喪屍片(含劇透)","createTime":"2020-09-23T20:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T11:53:25.000Z","uid":247527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2b48ac44da5aa378bdfae046fe8b79ac413943","tid":2215171,"uid":247527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:56:38.000Z","msg":"套戲係講女主角喺屋企醒返，出門口想搵鄰居但係發現鄰居完全唔理佢仲想攞嘢打佢<br />\n然後走佬入後樓梯打電話俾條仔，但係訊號差對方聽唔到女主角講咩<br />\n之後落停車場，有個男人揸車，見到女主角求救都唔停咁兜過咗女主角<br />\n迫於無奈女主角唯有步行去條仔屋企，沿途街上面都有好多喪屍<br />\n千辛萬苦去到條仔屋企發現佢偷食<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">下面劇透結局</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條仔見到女主角之後好撚驚，驚到完全溝通唔到，女主角望向塊鏡先發現原來自己一早感染咗做喪屍，喺後樓梯打電話聽唔到係因為喪屍冇語言能力，喺停車場個開車男人唔停係因為自己係喪屍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他唔記得了，好想睇返，求睇過既巴絲話我知套戲叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2541868daa075157cae2e4b9fd8c9c9d173f86c4","tid":2215171,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:00:50.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<br />\nlm"},{"pid":"5b6cb1f85a92abe5a0159b1f60e1f4c1b65234c5","tid":2215171,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:02:17.000Z","msg":"想睇"},{"pid":"4618e8620fc37ac307f25f45e0245c8e6e75767b","tid":2215171,"uid":2854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:19:59.000Z","msg":"知邊套,但唔記得咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1a2aa0b4027e29dc20cd0a31ac41dc5ad98eaa","tid":2215171,"uid":133387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://monsterzeronj.files.wordpress.com/2014/07/contracted.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmonsterzeronj.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fcontracted.jpg&h=028e5be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嚟部？ 話說佢有第二集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.g